desc: Dog Pound Apparel provides custom and personalized garments made for the Brothers of the Omega Psi Phi Fraternity, Inc. We offer personalized chapter shorts, jerseys, line shirts, satin line jackets, sweatshirts, and windbreakers. We specialize in embroidery, heat transfer vinyl, screen printing, and sublimation.

layout.text: Embroidered apparel MADE with you in mind!
